#CollegeAdmissionsScandal

column4: RT @DMAnews1 #BREAKING: Former university tennis coach Michael Center has pled guilty in connection w/ accepting a $100,000 bribe to secure the admission of a purported student-athlete to the university. Sentencing is scheduled for Oct. 30th. #CollegeAdmissionsScandal
